				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-11689113/scp-4313#post-4245798</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Sat, 11 May 2019 21:32:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>MaliceAforethought</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2902864</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is one of those articles that makes me envious that I can't write this sort of thing myself. It's wonderfully bizarre, but still manages to be terrifying, coherent, and intriguing at the same time, all while maintaining that sense of grand&#8230; <em>space-ness</em> that shows up in a lot of your stuff. It's genuinely astounding that you can still write scips like this without retreading the same old ground.</p> <p>Solid upvote :)</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
