					<![CDATA[
						 <p>At long last, new Ad Astra Per Aspera content.</p> <p>If anybody is curious this is based on the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pioneer_anomaly">Pioneer anomaly</a>, a phenomenon with a name so perfect that I just had to write something based on it. However, the actual explanation behind the anomaly is cool enough that I had to preserve it to some degree. That meant shelving the anomalous shenanigans on <em>Pioneer 11</em> rather than both probes. (<em>Pioneer 10</em> gets to live, for now)</p> <p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rattles" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4377609&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1557604716" alt="rattles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4377609)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/rattles" >rattles</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=462110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1557604716" alt="Tuomey Tombstone" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=462110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/tuomey-tombstone" >Tuomey Tombstone</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2902864&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1557604716" alt="MaliceAforethought" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2902864)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/maliceaforethought" >MaliceAforethought</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5028224&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1557604716" alt="Crashington" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5028224)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/crashington" >Crashington</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nyaaly" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5060953&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1557604716" alt="Nyaaly" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5060953)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nyaaly" >Nyaaly</a></span> for crit!</p> <p>Images:</p> <ul> <li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:An_artist%27s_impression_of_a_Pioneer_spacecraft_on_its_way_to_interstellar_space.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:An_artist%27s_impression_of_a_Pioneer_spacecraft_on_its_way_to_interstellar_space.jpg</a></li> <li><a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Meteor_burst.jpg">https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Meteor_burst.jpg</a></li> </ul> 
